# Demo: wts generate
# Usage: vhs demo-g.tape

Output demo-g.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set FontFamily "Cascadia Code"
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 150ms

Hide

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "wts g 'find files modified in the last week'"
Sleep 2s
Enter

Sleep 1s

Show
Sleep 2s

Down
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 2s
